e=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615406\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 25, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qhf1665702748352.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qhf1665702748352.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qhf1665702748352.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qhf1665702748352\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"qhf1665702748352__starting_and_stopping_the_sentinel_rms_license_manager_on_unix_and_linux_204908\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">To start or stop the RMS License Manager, use the following commands.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qhf1665702748352__li_d30500e1_d30501e1_d30502e1\">On Solaris: <p class=\"p\" id=\"qhf1665702748352__p_d67727e1_d67728e1_d67729e1\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">/etc/init.d/rms start</kbd>\n</p><p class=\"p\" id=\"qhf1665702748352__p_d67730e1_d67731e1_d67732e1\">\n<kbd class=\"ph userinput\">/etc/init.d/rms stop</kbd>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qhf1665702748352__li_d30503e1_d30504e1_d30505e1\">On Linux,\n            if your system uses <code class=\"ph codeph\">systemd</code>: <p class=\"p\" id=\"qhf1665702748352__p_d67733e1_d67734e1_d67735e1\">\n<kbd class=\"ph userinput\">systemctl start rms.target</kbd>\n</p><p class=\"p\" id=\"qhf1665702748352__p_d67736e1_d67737e1_d67738e1\">\n<kbd class=\"ph userinput\">systemctl stop rms.target</kbd>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qhf1665702748352__li_d30506e1_d30507e1_d30508e1\">On AIX: <p class=\"p\" id=\"qhf1665702748352__p_d67739e1_d67740e1_d67741e1\">\n<kbd class=\"ph userinput\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">InstallationDirectory</var>/rms.sh start</kbd>\n</p><p class=\"p\" id=\"qhf1665702748352__p_d67742e1_d67743e1_d67744e1\">\n<kbd class=\"ph userinput\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">InstallationDirectory</var>/rms.sh stop</kbd>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"qhf1665702748352__note_N10066_N10012_N10001\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> For cloud-served licenses, these commands start and stop both the RMS License Manager and the Cloud Plug-in at the same time and in the correct order.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qhf1665702748352__p_d67745e1_d67746e1_d67747e1\">When starting the RMS License Manager,  the following\n         output displays:</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><samp class=\"ph systemoutput sysout\">The RMS license server is running. </samp>\n</p>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615406\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615406\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Starting and Stopping the Sentinel RMS License Manager on Unix and Linux Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 25, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 To start or stop the RMS License Manager, use the following commands. On Solaris: /etc/init.d/rms start /etc/init.d/rms stop On Linux, if your system uses systemd : systemctl start rms.target systemctl stop rms.target On AIX: InstallationDirectory /rms.sh start InstallationDirectory /rms.sh stop Note: For cloud-served licenses, these commands start and stop both the RMS License Manager and the Cloud Plug-in at the same time and in the correct order. When starting the RMS License Manager, the following output displays: The RMS license server is running. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}